name: Set Codes
func:
//Game Status/Flash Code
flash = 0
if(msg.gamestatus.search('m') == -1){
    flash = 1
}
if(msg.gamestatus.substring(0, 3) == '4th'){
    flash = 2
}
if(msg.gamestatus.substring(0, 2) == 'OT'){
    flash = 2
}
if(msg.gamestatus == 'FINAL'){
    flash = 0
}

msg.flash = flash

//Light Code
if(parseFloat(msg.teamscore[0]) > parseFloat(msg.teamscore[1])){
    t0_light = 'G'
    t1_light = 'R'
}
if(parseFloat(msg.teamscore[0]) < parseFloat(msg.teamscore[1])){
    t0_light = 'R'
    t1_light = 'G'
}
if(parseFloat(msg.teamscore[0]) == parseFloat(msg.teamscore[1])){
    t0_light = 'Y'
    t1_light = 'Y'
}
if(msg.gamestatus.search('m') != -1){
    t0_light = 'P'
    t1_light = 'P'
}

msg.team0light = t0_light
